&lt;li&gt;Design streaming pipelines that close the loop between serving and learning, capturing impressions, clicks, and conversions in near real time so models retrain on fresh signal.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stand up and maintain a real-time feature store so features stay consistent between offline training and low-latency online inference.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the ad-event and attribution data backbone: clean, reconciled pipelines for delivery, billing, and third-party attribution partners.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner directly with data scientists to move models from notebook to production, owning the data contracts, freshness SLAs, and lineage they depend on.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build reusable, config-driven frameworks so new models and campaigns onboard without bespoke pipeline work each time.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Keep the platform reliable at scale: billions of events daily within defined SLAs, backed by monitoring, data-quality checks, and dependable backfills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set best practices and processes around pipeline design, testing, and data modeling across the team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
