&lt;li&gt;Experience working with large datasets on a major cloud provider (GCP preferred; AWS or Azure also fine).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solid software engineering fundamentals: testing, CI/CD with Git and Jenkins or similar, and code you would be happy to maintain.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfort working shoulder to shoulder with data scientists and ML engineers, and a clear understanding of what production ML needs from data - features, freshness, consistency, and lineage.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent problem-solving and communication skills, and the self-motivation to own problems end to end.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
